name: BrinezWorld Special Edition 4th of July Tee
description:
**SPECIAL EDITION**
**NOW SOLD OUT!**

Special quantities will be made available for a limited time. To place an order, contact us directly at BrinezWorldMedia@gmail.com with the subject: NewYorkAmerica 4th Tees.

Celebrate your independence with this one of a kind, special edition take on the BrinezWorld Trademark Logo and upcoming BrinezWorld "New York America" tee. Pick one up and celebrate your country all year round! Also available as a tank top.

If you’re looking for a shirt to set you apart from the rest, The BrinezWorld Special Edition 4th of July "New York America" Tee will do just the trick. With this special edition print, tackle the day in style!. Made from 100% super soft cotton, this tee will ensure your stylish and comfortable at the same time. 

The "New York America" tee due out this summer. 

Color Choice: Navy Blue w/ White and Red Print

Size Options: Small, Medium, Large, X-Large, XX-Large, XXX-Large. (sizes XX-XXX add $2.00)

Care: Machine Wash Cold, Tumble Dry Low
Material: 100% Cotton
Shipping: 1-8 days
Return Policy: This item is final sale and not eligible for return
